Real estate listings held by brokerage firms other than Zillow, Inc. are marked with the Internet Data Exchange logo and detailed information about them includes the name of the listing broker(s). data.description: Welcome to this wonderful brick home that has been loved, cared for, and offers something for everyone!  It boasts beautiful hardwood floors throughout and has a media space in the basement for entertaining.  With a privacy fence and your own garden, you can enjoy an amazing outdoor space and peaceful evenings in your backyard.  There is also a detached garage already setup with 220 electric ready for you next project.  Come see this home that truly offers a space for everyone!
